growing a planet.

00:44:06.160 --> 00:44:07.430
We're not growing food.

00:44:07.430 --> 00:44:09.270
We're growing soil.

00:44:09.270 --> 00:44:10.590
And we're not growing
just soil.

00:44:10.590 --> 00:44:14.240
We need to grow ecosystems.
