00:47:50.340 --> 00:47:50.660
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:47:50.660 --> 00:47:52.970
JOHN JEAVONS: Sure,
I'd be glad to.

00:47:52.970 --> 00:47:55.750
First of all, if you want to
reduce your water consumption

00:47:55.750 --> 00:48:00.870
per unit of calorie produced,
a really good

00:48:00.870 --> 00:48:02.720
crop to grow is potatoes.

00:48:02.720 --> 00:48:05.440
It produces a lot of calories
per unit of

00:48:05.440 --> 00:48:08.240
water per unit of time.

00:48:08.240 --> 00:48:12.360
Another crop that's fairly
efficient is carrots.

00:48:12.360 --> 00:48:13.290
I was surprised.

00:48:13.290 --> 00:48:14.740
I thought, carrots
